snippet.title: The June Brides | Event Trailer
snippet.description:
This June, confetti and petals are scattered across the Land of Dawn. The brides are already dressed in their finest, strolling ahead to express to you their sincere wishes as they join you upon a romantic date. The grand June Brides event is about to begin: are you ready?
Event Time: 06/03/2022 - 06/30/2022
